sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser (UaClient)
    participant WS as OpcUaWsServer
    participant S as OpcUaWsSession
    participant M as OpcUaWsSessionManager
    participant SEC as SecurityService

    Note over B,WS: TLS handshake, then WebSocket upgrade
    B->>WS: GET /ua<br/>Upgrade: websocket<br/>Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: opcua+uajson<br/>Origin: https://scada.local
    WS->>WS: validate subprotocol + allowed origin
    WS-->>B: 101 Switching Protocols

    WS->>S: create session state
    B->>S: CreateSessionRequest (JSON)
    S->>M: CreateSession(requestedTimeout)
    M-->>S: SessionId + AuthenticationToken + ServerNonce + RevisedTimeout
    S-->>B: CreateSessionResponse

    B->>S: ActivateSessionRequest<br/>(UserNameIdentityToken: PBKDF2(password, nonce))
    S->>M: ActivateSession(sessionId, token, credentials)
    M->>SEC: authenticate(user, token)
    SEC-->>M: identity accepted
    M-->>S: attached session + scada::ServiceContext
    S-->>B: ActivateSessionResponse

    Note over B,M: Data plane opens after the session is attached
    Note over B,S: Existing coroutine service-handler layer handles Read / Write / Browse / Translate / HistoryRead / Call / node management

    Note over B,S: Connection drops, browser reconnects before timeout
    S->>M: DetachSession(authenticationToken)
    B->>S: ActivateSessionRequest(sessionId, token)
    S->>M: ActivateSession(resume)
    M-->>S: resumed attached session
    S-->>B: ActivateSessionResponse(resumed=true)

    B->>S: CloseSessionRequest
    S->>M: CloseSession(sessionId, token)
    M-->>S: session removed
    S-->>B: CloseSessionResponse
    WS-->>B: Close frame (1000)
